{"tid":436984,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾意左補習個學生個阿爺","createTime":"2017-10-15T14:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T15:23:01.000Z","uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dbf134c56f420639242802466c63f7a7c80fd803","tid":436984,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T14:46:48.000Z","msg":"話說我而家幫緊個小三男仔補習<br />\n大家見我話鍾意佢阿爺可能覺得我痴線<br />\n但其實佢地成家都好後生<br />\n佢阿爺都係50歲倒<br />\n我第一日上到去 見倒佢已經覺得好有男人味<br />\n我鍾意d比較成熟既男人<br />\n成日補補下我都會偷望下佢<br />\n佢又會好溫柔咁對我 問我食唔食野口唔口渴果d<br />\n有一次個學生去左廁所<br />\n得我同佢兩個果陣 佢仲係咁讚我又白又長腿<br />\n搞到我勁怕醜<br />\n琴日我補完之後發覺對鞋個底爛左<br />\n之後佢即刻拎左佢對波鞋俾我著 size岩岩好<br />\n諗起都好warm<br />\n點算好 我知我唔應該咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353d62ac7607c771db99f3bc5db6ecb030c809d1","tid":436984,"uid":36696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T14:49:55.000Z","msg":"善用起式功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44e08dac0e33662711b3d605c960a8011cff7d6","tid":436984,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>善用起式功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"72e500a1c6871e62b42802ab700203b656b87927","tid":436984,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T14:51:41.000Z","msg":"之後佢即刻拎左佢對波鞋俾我著 <span style=\"color: red;\">size岩岩好</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1125d9c49141f84fe3e80bbb859de65b5e38283","tid":436984,"uid":4052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:20:57.000Z","msg":"互射12碼啦屌"},{"pid":"426342fc690bf580b7b1ff84d602a9489007e22d","tid":436984,"uid":36